ets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce902cf23dd9bca1f12a4002256f7d7c34ba490e","tid":2065554,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T15:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e8686eb5c858c064b02101afc5de5657b99fdb","tid":2065554,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T19:50:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">白領、餐飲、零售、炒散 <br />\n大學生 要人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>share ig fb wtsapp airdrop</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">［最後衝刺］620大三罷公投，公會極度要人，學生記得投票！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2065451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2065451</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</div>"},{"pid":"33cc501a847ff49b1b0b2d490565e4735f30f594","tid":2065554,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T09:36:54.000Z","msg":"轉載自白領工會fb<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCYbJGG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCYbJGG.png&h=31ea0fc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥門檻極低 人人都可以入白領工會🔥<br />\n想參與620既罷工罷課公投 ? 但又冇工會入? 🤔<br />\n唔緊要! 有我地白領工會! <br />\n白領工會橫跨各行各業, 只要你有用電腦做野, 有做paper work就係我地既準會員啦! <br />\n Yeah ✌️ 得咗<br />\n<br />\n入會表格：<br />\n<a href=\"http://application.hkwccu.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fapplication.hkwccu.org&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7oLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=7a0337cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://application.hkwccu.org</a><br />\n<br />\n請帶備<br />\n📑工作證明 及💰年費（現金$50 )黎街站搵我地啦<br />\n<br />\n今日街站<br />\n▶️荔枝角青山道650號益大工業大廈515室 (12n-2pm）<br />\n▶️黃竹坑黨鐵站B出口天橋 (7pm-9pm)<br />\n💡確認左會籍就可以參加6月20日既罷工公投啦！"}